TI  - Digital twins for smart building at the facility management stage: a systematic review of enablers, applications and challenges
PY  - 2025
T2  - Smart and Sustainable Built Environment
VL  - 14
IS  - 4
SP  - 1194
EP  - 1229
DO  - 10.1108/SASBE-10-2023-0298
