TI  - What Have Urban Digital Twins Contributed to Urban Planning and Decision Making? From a Systematic Literature Review Toward a Socio-Technical Research and Development Agenda
PY  - 2025
T2  - Smart Cities
VL  - 8
IS  - 1
C7  - 32
